Title: 整体架构
Describe: s20 将 19 种机制组织为 5 个架构层：执行层（Agent Loop）、工具层（Tool Pool）、服务层（Task/Cron/Background/MCP）、协作层（Team/Protocol）、安全层（Hook/Permission），通过 messages 列表和 context 字典作为核心数据通道连接。
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
系统分层架构

[Description]
从外到内的 5 层架构：

1. **CLI 入口层** — `__main__` REPL + cron_autorun_loop
2. **Agent 执行层** — `agent_loop` + `prepare_context` + `call_llm`
3. **工具调度层** — `assemble_tool_pool` + `BUILTIN_HANDLERS` + MCP handlers
4. **服务层** — Task / Worktree / Cron / Background / MCP / Skill / Memory
5. **安全 & 扩展层** — Hooks + Permission Pipeline

数据流向：用户输入 → messages → LLM → tool_use → handler → tool_result → messages → LLM ...

[UML]
@startuml
package "CLI 入口层" {
  [__main__ REPL]
  [cron_autorun_loop]
}

package "Agent 执行层" {
  [agent_loop]
  [prepare_context]
  [call_llm / with_retry]
  [error recovery]
}

package "工具调度层" {
  [assemble_tool_pool]
  [BUILTIN_HANDLERS (27)]
  [MCP handlers]
  [tool dispatch]
}

package "服务层" {
  [Task System]
  [Worktree System]
  [Cron Scheduler]
  [Background Tasks]
  [MCP System]
  [Skill Loading]
  [Context Compaction]
  [Subagent]
  [Teammate Thread]
}

package "安全 & 扩展层" {
  [Hook Pipeline]
  [Permission Check]
  [Prompt Assembly]
}

[__main__ REPL] --> [agent_loop]
[cron_autorun_loop] --> [agent_loop]
[agent_loop] --> [prepare_context]
[agent_loop] --> [call_llm / with_retry]
[agent_loop] --> [tool dispatch]
[tool dispatch] --> [assemble_tool_pool]
[tool dispatch] --> [Hook Pipeline]
[assemble_tool_pool] --> [BUILTIN_HANDLERS (27)]
[assemble_tool_pool] --> [MCP handlers]
[BUILTIN_HANDLERS (27)] --> [Task System]
[BUILTIN_HANDLERS (27)] --> [Worktree System]
[BUILTIN_HANDLERS (27)] --> [Cron Scheduler]
[BUILTIN_HANDLERS (27)] --> [Subagent]
[BUILTIN_HANDLERS (27)] --> [Teammate Thread]
[BUILTIN_HANDLERS (27)] --> [Skill Loading]
[agent_loop] --> [error recovery]
[prepare_context] --> [Context Compaction]
@enduml

[Detail]
分层的核心原则是**关注点分离**：Agent Loop 不知道具体工具实现细节，只通过 `handlers[name](**args)` 分发；工具 handler 不知道上下文管理策略；Hook 管道可以拦截任何工具而不修改工具代码。这种解耦使得添加新工具只需在 `BUILTIN_TOOLS` 和 `BUILTIN_HANDLERS` 各加一条记录。

------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
线程模型

[Description]
s20 运行时共有 4 类线程：

| 线程 | 类型 | 生命周期 | 作用 |
|------|------|---------|------|
| Main Thread | 主线程 | 进程生命周期 | REPL + agent_loop |
| cron_scheduler_loop | daemon | 持久 | 每秒检查 cron 表达式 |
| cron_autorun_loop | daemon | 持久 | 无人值守时执行 fired jobs |
| Teammate threads | daemon | 按需创建 | 独立 LLM 对话循环 |
| Background workers | daemon | 短命 | 执行慢操作 |

**线程安全措施**:
- `agent_lock` — 保护 `agent_loop` 不被主线程和 autorun 并发调用
- `background_lock` — 保护 `background_tasks` / `background_results` 字典
- `cron_lock` — 保护 `scheduled_jobs` / `cron_queue`

[UML]
@startuml
concurrency

rectangle "Main Thread" as main {
  (REPL Loop)
  (agent_loop)
}

rectangle "Cron Scheduler\n(daemon)" as cronThread {
  (cron_scheduler_loop)
  (每秒扫描 scheduled_jobs)
}

rectangle "Cron Autorun\n(daemon)" as autoThread {
  (cron_autorun_loop)
  (consume_cron_queue → agent_loop)
}

rectangle "Teammate\n(daemon, N个)" as tmThread {
  (独立 LLM 循环)
  (idle_poll 等待)
}

rectangle "Background Worker\n(daemon, 短命)" as bgThread {
  (执行慢操作)
  (结果写入 background_results)
}

database "共享状态" as shared {
  (history: list)
  (scheduled_jobs: dict)
  (cron_queue: list)
  (background_tasks: dict)
  (active_teammates: dict)
}

main --> shared : agent_lock
cronThread --> shared : cron_lock
autoThread --> shared : agent_lock
bgThread --> shared : background_lock
tmThread --> shared : MessageBus (文件)
@enduml

[Detail]
线程模型的设计权衡：(1) 用 `threading.Lock` 而非 `asyncio`——保持代码同步风格，对教学更友好；(2) Teammate 通过文件信箱（MessageBus）而非内存队列通信——更接近生产系统的进程间通信模式；(3) Background worker 是 fire-and-forget 模式，结果通过 `collect_background_results()` 在下一轮 LLM 调用前注入。

------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
子系统连接关系

[Description]
19 个子系统之间的核心依赖关系：

- **Agent Loop** 依赖所有其他系统（是最终的编排者）
- **Tool Pool** 合并 Builtin + MCP 工具
- **Teammate** 依赖 Task（claim/complete）、MessageBus（通信）、Worktree（工作目录）
- **Cron** 依赖 Agent Loop（注入 fired jobs 后执行）
- **Background** 依赖 Tool Handlers（实际执行）+ Agent Loop（结果通知）
- **Error Recovery** 依赖 Context Compaction（reactive compact）
- **Permission** 拦截所有工具调用（PreToolUse hook）

[UML]
@startuml
component [Agent Loop] as loop #Gold
component [Tool Pool] as pool
component [Task System] as task
component [Worktree] as wt
component [Cron Scheduler] as cron
component [Background Tasks] as bg
component [Teammate Thread] as tm
component [MessageBus] as bus
component [Protocol State] as proto
component [Hook Pipeline] as hooks
component [Context Compaction] as compact
component [Error Recovery] as recovery
component [MCP System] as mcp
component [Skill Loading] as skill
component [Prompt Assembly] as prompt
component [Subagent] as sub

loop --> pool : 获取工具
loop --> compact : prepare_context
loop --> recovery : with_retry
loop --> cron : consume_cron_queue
loop --> bg : collect_background_results
loop --> hooks : PreToolUse / PostToolUse
loop --> prompt : assemble_system_prompt

pool --> mcp : 合并 MCP 工具
pool --> task : handler
pool --> wt : handler
pool --> tm : handler
pool --> sub : handler
pool --> skill : handler
pool --> cron : handler
pool --> bg : should_run_background

tm --> bus : send / read_inbox
tm --> task : claim / complete
tm --> wt : cwd 切换
tm --> proto : submit_plan

hooks --> pool : 拦截调用
recovery --> compact : reactive_compact
prompt --> skill : list_skills
prompt --> mcp : 连接状态
@enduml

[Detail]
这张依赖图展示了 s20 的"星型"架构——`agent_loop` 在中心，所有子系统围绕它运作。关键的设计决策是**不使用依赖注入框架**，而是通过全局变量（如 `mcp_clients`、`scheduled_jobs`、`active_teammates`）和函数调用实现连接。这是教学代码的有意简化，生产系统会引入依赖注入容器。
